title: Hanes Men's Max Cushioned Ankle Socks, Multipacks
description: COMFORT YOU DESERVE – Max cushioning of the foot make these cushioned socks for men a sure bet for everyday wear, from work, play, gym, sports, and beyond.

EXTRA DURABLE – Our socks are made to be durable, but these socks are made to be Double Tough. During testing, these socks are able to withstand more than twice the number of rubs than our regular socks, making them extra resistant to holes!
KEEP YOUR COOL - Cool Comfort fabric wicks away moisture so your feet stay cool and dry all day.
FRESH ALL DAY - Fresh IQ advanced odor protection technology
SMOOTH SEAMS – Comfort Toe seams are our smoothest seams yet
EASY CARE – Throw your new socks right in the washing machine on laundry day. Wash on cold and save!

Hanes Men's Max Cushion Ankle socks will keep you comfortable all day. These socks are not only comfortable, but are durable as well, with Double Tough Durability. Wicking Cool Comfort Fabric will help keep your feet cool and dry. FreshIQ Advanced Odor Technology helps fight stinky feet! Spandex and Comfort Toe Seam will provide comfort and a better fit.
